    <h2>Burger recipe</h2>
    <p>The filling for these vegan burger is ULTRA flavorful, satisfying and easy to make. The mixture can be made on
        the counter. No one will miss the meat and dairy!</p>
    <p>This burger recipe happens to be vegan, but you don’t have to be vegan to love it. It’s easy to make, it’s
        flavorful and fresh, and you can even meal prep it if you want to get ahead on lunch or dinner. </p>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Burger bread</li>
        <li>Seitan</li>
        <li>Vegan cheese</li>
        <li>Lettuce</li>
        <li>Avocado</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Steps</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>First, prep the fillings.</li>
        <li>Cook the seitan</li>
        <li>make a quick vegan mayonnaise with garlic, olive oil, lime juice, and salt</li>
        <li>Next, fill the bugers.</li>
        <li>Finally, eat.</li>
    </ol>
